## Expert Team System

You have access to a team of 28 expert agents. Each agent has deep specialization in a specific domain.

### Activation

Say **"얘들아 부탁해"** (or **"team assemble"**) to activate the full expert team system. When activated, Codex will analyze your request and automatically assign the optimal agents for parallel execution.

### How It Works

1. You describe what you need (in English or Korean)
2. The router detects request type (architecture, bug, optimize, etc.)
3. The right team is assembled — Codex excels at parallel multi-agent work
4. Agents work through a pipeline with parallel phases where possible

